criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. The patients conform to the diagnostic criteria of allergic rhinitis;

          2. Sex unlimited;

          3. To be aged from 5-70;

          4. The course of the disease in more than one year

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Do not conform the inclusion criteria;

          2. The patients who allergic to adhesive plaster, drugs and application materials; The
             people who has scar constitution and skin injuries;

          3. The people who has chronic sinusitis History;

          4. The people who has paroxysmal disease of respiratory system like asthma;

          5. The people who accept the treatment of specific immunity therapy and system hormone
             therapy in recent a year;

          6. Pregnant women and nursing mothers;

          7. Tuberculosis and hepatitis patients; The people who's Ur, ALT, AST is higher than the
             normal value 2 times;

          8. The people who have mental disease;

          9. The people who smoking to more than 10 cigarettes per day for 10 years;

         10. the people who has other problem which is not suitable to participate in this project
             study
